{"title":"---","markdown":{"headingText":"---","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"# Draft Technical Specification for the Package\n\n## 1. Overview\n\nA Python package to abstract and unify access to AI/ML resources, tools, and\ndata for subsea computer vision projects, supporting distributed processing and\nlarge-scale data management.\n\n## 2. Core Features\n\n- **Resource Abstraction:**  \n  Unified APIs for AWS, Azure, GCP, Databricks, and Petrobras on-premises storage.\n\n- **Data Ingestion:**  \n  - Secure, scalable ingestion of images, videos, and reports;\n  - support for batch and streaming.\n- **Distributed Processing:**  \n  - Integration with Spark (Databricks), Dask, and cloud-native batch/streaming\n    services for parallel processing.\n\n- **Experiment Management:**  \n  - Tracking, comparison, and versioning of datasets, models, and results;\n  - automated logging of metrics and artifacts.\n\n- **Feature Engineering:**  \n  Modular pipelines for preprocessing, augmentation, annotation, and feature\n  extraction from media and reports.\n\n- **Storage & Retrieval:**  \n  - Efficient storage, retrieval, and indexing of large-scale media and metadata;\n  - metadata management for traceability.\n\n- **Security & Compliance:**  \n  - Authentication, authorization, and audit logging;\n  - compliance with Petrobras standards.\n\n- **Documentation & Usability:**  \n  Comprehensive documentation, example notebooks, and best practices for subsea\n  CV workflows.\n\n## 3. Architecture\n\n- **Ingestion Layer:** APIs and connectors for data sources\n- **Processing Layer:** Distributed engines (Spark, Dask, etc.)\n- **Feature Store:** Centralized storage for engineered features\n- **Experiment Tracker:** Integrated with MLflow or similar tools\n- **Governance Layer:** Security, compliance, and audit modules\n\n## 4. Extensibility\n\n- Modular design for easy integration of new tools, data types, and workflows.\n\n## 5. Testing & Quality\n\n- ≥80% code coverage in unit tests\n- Automated integration and performance tests\n\n## 6. Deployment\n\n- Containerized for cloud and on-premises environments\n- CI/CD pipelines for automated builds and releases\n\n## 7. Documentation\n\n- User guides, API references, and example workflows\n\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":true,"echo":false,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":true,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true,"produce-source-notebook":true,"notebook-preserve-cells":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","toc":true,"output-file":"package.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-links-title":"Other Links","code-lin